body: I've just seen the same error on 0.9.0 on Ubuntu 14.04

The panic is benign, even though it looks nasty - it's the GUI looking for updates on an item at the same time it's being removed (because someone disconnected).

The ping timeouts ought to be simply network related. How slow is your network?
Slight modification to this - the panic _is_ benign, but the fact that it happens is actually worrying. It shouldn't, as far as I can tell...
